titleStmt.title: A true and exact list of the members of both houses of this present convocation, summon'd to meet on the sixth day of November, A.D. 1689. in the chapter-house at St. Paul's, and from thence adjourned to Henry the VII's chappel at Westminster, to the twentieth day of the same month.
